ingredients: POTATOES, VEGETABLE OIL (CONTAINS ONE OR MORE OF THE FOLLOWING OILS: CANOLA, SOYBEAN, COTTONSEED, SUNFLOWER, CORN), BLEACHED ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLOAVIN, FOLIC ACID). CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF ANNATTO (COLOR), BAKING SODA, DEXTRIN, DEXTROSE, EXTRACTIVES OF PAPRIKA (COLOR), EXTRACTIVES OF CAPSICUM, GARLIC POWDER, ONION POWDER, PAPRIKA (COLOR), SALT, SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE (MAINTAINS NATURAL COLOR & LEAVENING), SPICES, TAPIOCA STARCH, TAPIOCA STARCH-MODIFIED, XANTHAN GUM.
